PrecisAuthority to enter into SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENTS with (a) the Provinces of Newfoundland, Nova Scotia, Ontario and Prince Edward Island, in order to extend various AGRICULTURAL SAFETY NET COMPANION AGREEMENTS for one year beyond their current expiry date of March 31, 1999, and (b) the Province of NOVA SCOTIA in order to extend the AGRICULTURAL SAFETY NET MANAGEMENT AGREEMENT for two years (1998-99 and 1999-2000).
